premise_source_doc_sentence: The Story of Bohemian Rhapsody is a 2004 documentary about the song `` Bohemian Rhapsody '' , written by the lead singer of Queen , Freddie Mercury .
In 1975 , the British rock band Queen released `` Bohemian Rhapsody '' , a bombastic mock-operatic rock song which is in the form of a four-part suite but performed with rock instrumentation .
`` Bohemian Rhapsody '' is a song by the British rock band Queen .
